cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is about image synthesis using a denoising Generative Adversarial Network (GAN) and semantic layouts. The paper discusses the challenges of enhancing image quality while maintaining the stochasticity of the GAN, and generating overlapped objects. These topics are closely related to computer vision (cs.CV), graphics (cs.GR), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.MM, in that order.
